{"tid":449267,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點香薰起火　29歲女電召母求救","createTime":"2017-10-27T05:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T14:42:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c7a59048034dd4d550ef496b91866e0feecacec6","tid":449267,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:02:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171027/20195859\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F20195859&d=fW%2FbMTssWaiVGVkll%2FHuLcmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=8dbb6485\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F20195859&h=a558ec91\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171027/20195859</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點香薰起火　29歲女電召母求救<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】觀塘翠屏南邨一名29歲女子，通宵在客廳燃點香薰，其間失火燒着雜物引起火警，在房間熟睡的女事主被濃煙嗆醒，躲在房內致電母親報警，消防員到場將火撲熄並救出女事主，她吸入濃煙不適但拒絕送院，火警原因無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171027/large/1026wongkk_mg_9110.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171027%2Flarge%2F1026wongkk_mg_9110.jpg&h=e7b91512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廚房玻璃窗飛脫直墮街上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n母返家開門給消防救女<br />\n<br />\n現場為翠屏南邨翠榮樓16樓一單位，當時屋內只有29歲姓鄺女子在房間中睡覺，客廳則通宵燃點着香薰，至清晨約5時許，鄺女被濃煙嗆醒，走出房間查看，發現客廳中的香薰爐起火，並燒着旁邊的雜物，鄺女立即躲回房間致電通知母親報警，鄺母趕返家開門給消防員入屋，消防救出在房間的鄺女，並於約20分鐘後將火救熄。火場面積約6米乘8米，廚房一隻玻璃窗飛脫直墮街上，幸無傷人。<br />\n<br />\n過往本港亦曾發生多宗燃點香薰引致火警的意外，本月2日，粉嶺馬適路馬屎埔村一間堆滿雜物的木搭村屋，一名20歲女子點香薰驅蚊，燒着雜物起火，一家三口睡夢中險葬身火海。去年8月12日，灣仔堅彌地街康福樓一個單位，一名澳洲男租客燃點香薰引起火警，大門被烈燄濃煙攔阻，事主被困住所露台數分鐘險命喪火海，幸消防員趕至將他救出。<br />\n<br />\n市面大部份香薰油屬易燃液體，處理時須特別小心，消防處對此有多項指引，包括不要接近火源；不要把明火香薰爐放近易燃雜物及窗旁；點燃香薰後切勿離開。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃江奇、劉永明"},{"pid":"cfec2cfd6ff85a7b8af96877b225f1aa3907147d","tid":449267,"uid":1195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:07:58.000Z","msg":"白痴中女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec4fa69272afb54226c9cfecefbe87183c0438a","tid":449267,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:09:49.000Z","msg":"識打電話俾老母<br />\n唔識得報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e89593b978defdd8f052ae3015a10e7aa32f7ec","tid":449267,"uid":134864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:11:55.000Z","msg":"On9女人"},{"pid":"11ea50c4167e1a8d0cdd28c3788245ce0d4d703a","tid":449267,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"唔第一時間報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01a35ad5885ca66cac88fb1e9bd4e1af2044bd3","tid":449267,"uid":6473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:46:56.000Z","msg":"仲要匿返入房打電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7d5d96aaba5d4756cd16bcb0d6f0cab5b18ffb","tid":449267,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:48:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1a247e5ea05a3502a06057cace6cbce3b329fc1","tid":449267,"uid":124162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T06:58:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲要匿返入房打電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有一掌打撚左個窗落街通風先嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b7fa2cc7a19d01db9b30f0dbdaa51fd6248593","tid":449267,"uid":6473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲要匿返入房打電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有一掌打撚左個窗落街通風先嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通風定諗住跳落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16625fa7c258eb9a2f13dc74b914dc35ead0ad2","tid":449267,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:22:37.000Z","msg":"點解可以燒到成間屋 .. ? 好多易燃物定點"},{"pid":"bb6f3c302b34bb7168be9a4baefb3910dd22a669","tid":449267,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:37:42.000Z","msg":"有無咁撚蠢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652bacbfc9e92bd69b64f7b1c86e8cc127d1a14e","tid":449267,"uid":20117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"似有精神問題多啲，要屋企人幫先得那種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}